(Atho Consensus \(Current\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Date: 2026-04-18) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(This document defines the active consensus rules for the current Atho payment-only redesign.) Tj
T*
(- Active Protocol Profile) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The active chain is:) Tj
T*
(- payment-focused public/private UTXO) Tj
T*
(- 5 decimal precision) Tj
T*
(- deterministic fixed-point emissions) Tj
T*
(- no staking) Tj
T*
(- no bonding) Tj
T*
(- no BPoW role gating) Tj
T*
(- no premine) Tj
T*
(- no fee burn) Tj
T*
(- no consensus fee-pool routing) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Anything in older docs that describes stake/bond/BPoW validation, lockup state machines,) Tj
T*
(slashing, payout-set routing, or tail-burn economics is historical and not active consensus.) Tj
T*
(- Core Constants) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(From const.py:) Tj
T*
(- Block target time: 120 seconds) Tj
T*
(- Difficulty retarget interval: 180 blocks) Tj
T*
(- Standard transaction confirmations required: 6) Tj
T*
(- Private transaction confirmations required: 6) Tj
T*
(- Coinbase maturity: 150) Tj
T*
(- Max block base bytes: 3,500,000) Tj
T*
(- Max block weight: 14,000,000) Tj
T*
(- Max tx policy size \(vsize\): 250,000) Tj
T*
(- Display precision: 5 decimals) Tj
T*
(- 1 ATHO = 100,000 atoms) Tj
T*
(- Fee floor: 1 atom/vB) Tj
T*
(- Minimum transaction fee: 500 atoms) Tj
T*
(- Dust limit: 1 atom) Tj
T*
(- Max supply: 1,000,000,000.00000 ATHO) Tj
T*
(- Premine: 0) Tj
T*
(- Supply floor: 0) Tj
T*
(- Address and Ownership Rules) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Active public address role derivation is regular-only:) Tj
T*
(- regular: SHA3-384\("ATHO_ADDR_V1" || network || pubkey\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Consensus no longer recognizes bond or stake address roles as active ownership classes. Public) Tj
T*
(UTXO ownership and wallet derivation are payment-only.) Tj
T*
(- Transaction Consensus Path) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Primary code:) Tj
T*
(- Src/Main/txveri.py) Tj
T*
(- Src/Transactions/txvalidation.py) Tj
T*
() Tj
