(Consensus checks include:) Tj
T*
(- canonical serialization and hash consistency) Tj
T*
(- Falcon signature validity) Tj
T*
(- UTXO existence and unspent state) Tj
T*
(- no in-block or mempool double spend) Tj
T*
(- strict integer conservation in atoms) Tj
T*
(- fee floor enforcement by canonical vsize) Tj
T*
(- minimum transaction fee enforcement) Tj
T*
(- payment-owner derivation consistency) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Removed from the active path:) Tj
T*
(- bond deposits and withdrawals) Tj
T*
(- stake deposits and withdrawals) Tj
T*
(- bonded miner eligibility checks) Tj
T*
(- slash-trigger evaluation) Tj
T*
(- bond/stake-specific output role checks) Tj
T*
(- Private Layer Rules) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Private-layer checks remain consensus-critical:) Tj
T*
(- private nullifier uniqueness and replay protection) Tj
T*
(- anchor age and Merkle path validation) Tj
T*
(- note ownership and signature checks) Tj
T*
(- block proof-gate validation) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(PrivateTx now inherits the same active monetary and fee profile as public sends:) Tj
T*
(- 6 practical confirmations) Tj
T*
(- 1 atom/vB fee floor) Tj
T*
(- 500 atom minimum transaction fee) Tj
T*
(- no special fee-pool or stake-routing behavior) Tj
T*
(- Block Consensus Path) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Primary code:) Tj
T*
(- Src/Main/blockveri.py) Tj
T*
(- Src/Main/consensus.py) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Block acceptance enforces:) Tj
T*
(- parent linkage and index continuity) Tj
T*
(- PoW target validation) Tj
T*
(- merkle and witness-commitment checks) Tj
T*
(- byte and weight limits) Tj
T*
(- coinbase payout invariants) Tj
T*
(- transaction list validity under active tx rules) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Removed from the active block path:) Tj
T*
(- BPoW miner metadata enforcement) Tj
T*
(- bonded miner role-tag enforcement) Tj
T*
(- active-bond eligibility checks) Tj
T*
(- stake/bond payout accounting) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The miner signature payload still exists as canonical block metadata, but it is no longer tied) Tj
T*
(to bonded-role activation logic.) Tj
